    "patch_code": "private void find\u522b\u540d(Node traversal) {\n  S Scop = traversal.getScop();\n  for (var v : Scop.get iterable()) {\n    node n = v.getNode();\n int type = n.get type();\n    node parent = n.get parent();\n    if (parent.is Var()) {\n      if (n.has children() && n.get first child().is Qualified\u540d()) {\n      String name = n.getString();\n      Var\u522b\u540d Var = Scop.get Var(name);\n     \u522b\u540d. put(name,\u522b\u540d Var);\n\n      String qualifiedName =\n         \u522b\u540d Var.get initial value().get Qualified\u540d();\n      transformations.add\u522b\u540d(name, qualifyingName);\n      //bleeding functions already get a BAD_PARAMETers error, so just\n      //do nothing.\n      // parameters of the scop function also get a BAD_PARAMeters\n      //error.\n    } else {\n      //Queue non-animal variable or non-animal function\n      report(traversal, n, GLOBals. Scop_ non-\u522b\u540d_local, n.getString());\n    }\n    }\n  }\n}",
